room_title: Escape room "Titanic Room" by Escape Room Palm Springs in Palm Springs
room_address: 2500 N. Palm Canyon Dr., #B3, Palm Springs, CA 92262
room_description: You are searching for the key to a lifeboat with only 60 minutes before the ship sinks. The key is hidden in the Captain’s Stateroom and is reserved for any royalty that might be on board. Some say the Captain probably has it around his neck. No, he wouldn’t keep it there where it could be taken by force. He is a clever man and he would hide it somewhere secret... in his quarters.
